data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 5-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom modern marvel, offering an impressive 4,235 square feet of luxurious living space. Built in 2015 by the renowned luxury builder Bakerfield, this masterpiece represents the Cordova home model, elevated to new heights with a multitude of carefully curated upgrades. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by grandeur, with 8-foot doorways and soaring 12-foot ceilings that create an immediate sense of spaciousness. Dark, rich real wood floors flow seamlessly throughout, lending an air of sophistication to this remarkable home. The formal dining room features coffered ceilings, adding an elegant touch to your dining experience. The heart of this home is the chef's dream kitchen, boasting real wood cabinets, granite countertops, and top-of-the-line Professional KitchenAid appliances. A generously sized island provides ample workspace, and an upgraded coffee bar is a delightful addition for coffee connoisseurs. Abundant cabinet space ensures your culinary essentials are neatly organized. The open living room is adorned with a captivating stone wall and a built-in entertainment center, creating a cozy yet stylish atmosphere. The kitchen/living room combo offers an ideal setting for entertaining friends and family, with sliders providing direct access to the rear patio. As the seasons change, leave the sliders open to seamlessly blend indoor and outdoor living. The back patio is an oasis of its own, complete with a convenient half bathroom for guests. Step through the double doors to discover the owner's suite, featuring an extra-large wing with direct access to the patio. The owner’s suite also offers a bonus corner perfect for morning coffee, reading, or lounging. Sunlight bathes the entire home, infusing it with warmth and positivity. The master bathroom is a sanctuary with tile flooring, a sumptuous soaking tub, a walk-in shower with built-in shower heads, including a rainfall shower head. Two sizable walk-in closets with real wood flooring and built-in shelving cater to your wardrobe needs. A double vanity adds practicality to luxury. From the master bathroom, you have direct access to the laundry room, ensuring convenience at its finest. The first floor also includes three additional guest bedrooms and two full bathrooms, providing space and comfort for guests or family members. Upstairs, a bonus loft is perfect for entertaining, while a custom movie theater awaits, complete with surround sound, a subwoofer, and wiring for electronic blinds. A built-in granite counter and wet bar with a mini fridge ensure your guests are entertained in style within the movie theater. The second floor also houses another guest bedroom and a full bathroom. Step onto the covered balcony, a private retreat with scenic views of the pond, trees, and conservation lot to the left, creating a serene backdrop for relaxation.  Why wait for new construction when this luxury custom home is available now? Embrace the lifestyle you deserve in this meticulously designed oasis of comfort and sophistication. Your dream home awaits!
